Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:07.34,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,Shoyo is also watching
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.83,0:00:10.48,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,as the student he sacrificed \Nhis life to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:14.16,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,falls apart without protecting a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.52,0:00:15.49,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:18.00,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:20.62,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Gintoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:31.52,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:34.63,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here \Nso late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:37.77,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, could you please \Nshow me your license?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.01,0:02:10.90,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry, My Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:12.99,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Oboro?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:18.40,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping to watch those \Nrebels meet their demise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.64,0:02:21.46,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,The crows are astir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:24.41,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that there's \Nbeen a shift in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:26.54,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:27.68,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Those rebels are already...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:34.96,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:37.38,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,This is the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:40.49,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,What are you people doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:43.10,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,If you screw up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:46.10,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,We'll lose our heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:48.32,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:58.11,Ep Title,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,Pinky Swear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:02:59.43,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.43,0:03:01.16,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Why are the Mimawarigumi \Ninside the palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:03.12,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:06.64,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,You serve the Bakufu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:10.62,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,You're police officers, yet you assist \Nthe rebels, you traitorous scum?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:12.05,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Assist the rebels?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:15.26,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make false accusations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:20.08,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,There was an order to execute \Nthose criminals in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:23.70,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,If you're trying to dispatch \Nthem before the sun is up,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:27.80,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,you would be the ones \Ndefying the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:30.92,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Our lord ordered us to guard
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:33.20,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,the criminals until the \Nexecution takes place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:39.90,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it is our duty \Nto protect them until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:41.90,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kondo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:44.41,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,You rural samurai don't get to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:47.79,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten who let you \Ncountry bumpkins keep your swords?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:51.28,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,And now you're biting the \Nhand that feeds you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:53.55,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're lower than rebel \Nscum, you animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:55.29,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with being an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:04:00.30,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,Beats being a dog that wags \Nits tail at fat pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:03.66,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,When a fat pig is lying \Non the ground before you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.14,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,it gets eaten by
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:07.14,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,the wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:09.49,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me a pig, \Nyou punk Chihuahua!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:11.22,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't talking about you, Miss Piggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:12.02,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}was{\i0} about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:15.57,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Were you the ones who let the \NMimawarigumi inside the palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:20.53,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Has Sasaki joined forces with the \NShinsengumi to start a coup d'etat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:26.70,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Who joined forces with who \Nto start a what d'etat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:28.66,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you repeat that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:30.49,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Have you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:33.76,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? I couldn't hear you. What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:34.68,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,...and the Mimawarigumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:38.43,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,I said that I can't hear you! Yell it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:39.81,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,...joined forces?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:42.46,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Can't hear a thing! And I'm \Nnot interested in hearing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:44.55,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,You make me want to throw up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:46.65,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Who would join forces \Nwith those losers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:47.76,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Toshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:48.80,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Kondo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.55,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,We've got them inside the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:52.47,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Let's torch 'em with Sadasada!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:54.11,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! That wasn't part of the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:55.73,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Hell, you're sounding \Nlike one of the Joi now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:58.73,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it! Kill 'em all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.74,0:05:03.36,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it appears that \Nthey've gotten started.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:08.71,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, the palace has \Nbeen surrounded by us elites.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:13.37,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I told them to drop their weapons \Nand surrender, but I was lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:15.87,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:18.63,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't drop your weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:21.44,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,It would look bad if the cops
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:24.88,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,were to slaughter a \Nbunch of unarmed people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:26.88,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:28.39,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:31.82,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Nobume-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:36.44,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for carrying out your \Nmission alone while I was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.05,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a donut for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:44.78,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,You see, being an elite, I was \Nable to avoid a lethal blow,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.93,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,but it took a while to remove \Nthe poison from my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:51.45,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was still easier than \Nremoving a curry udon stain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:57.25,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,And it appears that you took good \Ncare of our Nobume, Sakata-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:00.33,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:02.33,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,They only got in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:03.84,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,You can't blame them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:08.78,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Nobume-san, they're ordinary \Npeople, unlike us elites.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:13.85,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,But it appears that he won't be \Nof any more use at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:15.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:19.30,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The elite must be really \Nspecial to need help
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:22.61,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,from the ordinary to make it back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:25.54,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't by choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:28.32,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,A certain person requested \Nthat we work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:33.15,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,And we are simply using each \Nother to ensure our survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:35.74,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy of my enemy is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:37.12,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:40.62,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably too difficult for \Nyou ordinary folk to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:45.37,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Essentially, it's like Nobita and \NGian in the Doraemon movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:50.08,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Two rivals who will use each other\N to achieve the same purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:52.64,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,when faced with a crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:56.48,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Doraemon isn't such a dark story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:58.14,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:08.36,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Sakata-san, you are useless trash now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:14.37,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've disposed of that \Ngarbage, let's clean this place up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:19.37,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:22.29,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Gintoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:23.46,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:24.29,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ginto—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:34.35,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Gintoki, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.31,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.56,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,It's a form of acupuncture.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.91,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,His body will still feel numb for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:42.77,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,but at least he'll be able to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:45.39,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I also injected some serum into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:47.82,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,The elite never miss a step.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:50.82,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Consider my debt paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:54.23,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go back to the \Nother ordinary people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:58.17,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,If you stick around, you'll end up \Nbeing taken out with the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:01.33,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:06.84,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're not giving me any interest \Nafter taking this long to get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:09.00,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Begging for more again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:10.38,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:18.65,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Sadasada's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.16,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:24.90,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot of interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:27.40,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, his head's worth nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:36.57,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I have an order for the Mimawarigumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:41.34,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,All elites will begin supporting \Nthat ordinary man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:46.13,Main01,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,On our pride as elites, we must not \Nallow a single person to go upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:51.59,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,You won't listen if I tell you that \Nyour body can't take any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:53.44,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm coming with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:55.48,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you break our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:58.10,Main01,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,That goes for you and Maizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:09:00.10,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Time for the last stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:02.93,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you hog the glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:07.62,Main01,Nobu,0000,0000,0000,,The last bite of a donut \Nis always the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:21.21,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:23.27,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinsengumi and Mimawarigumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:26.67,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,the two largest police forces \Nin Edo, have joined forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:30.65,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,I was told that they were rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:34.16,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem that someone \Nhas brought them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:36.56,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,The ship will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:38.43,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,You should escape, for your own safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:40.64,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,My Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:45.13,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Are they serious about \Ntaking over this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:49.21,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I must respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:55.50,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Summon every remaining police \Nforce to the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:58.99,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,We'll crush them with all of our might.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:04.58,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:06.31,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,B-Big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:07.96,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,There are armies attacking \Nthe north and south gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:10.00,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! Who are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:11.37,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:13.22,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Clear me a path in three seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:15.41,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,or else I blow down the gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:16.76,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.38,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to two and three?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:22.64,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:27.02,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,A man only needs the number \None to get through life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:30.27,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The entire police force?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.47,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:34.31,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,The police are rebelling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:36.28,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's absolutely absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,0:10:38.76,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,This is no uprising!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:41.28,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's capable of bringing \Nall these men together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:43.78,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,There's one person who can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:47.75,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,One person capable of ordering \Nthe police, or anyone, around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:51.67,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't understand \Nwhat this is, Lord Sadasada?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:07.93,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,You are the traitor who has betrayed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:09.59,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:13.44,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Shigeshige... So you're behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:16.94,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,My Lord! What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:18.68,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,Lower your weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:20.95,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,We've wasted too much time fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:24.75,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,You men are valuable soldiers \Nwho defend this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.13,0:11:27.91,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow you to \Nthrow your lives away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:29.89,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, My Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:31.93,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,We have orders from Sadasada-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:33.09,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,Were you not listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:36.30,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to drop your weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:51.77,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,Will you clear a path for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:57.95,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,My Lord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:11:59.01,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:01.53,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,They're rebel scum who \Nwronged our country!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:03.53,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to approach them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:09.79,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shogun-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:13.17,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,My shortcomings have caused \Nyou so much suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.68,0:12:14.83,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,Let me offer you my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:19.80,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for defending \Nmy loyal retainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:22.98,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for you, I would have...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:28.03,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,We would have allowed the beloved \Nman who raised us to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.32,0:12:29.89,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,Grampy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:33.85,Main01,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:36.01,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,Grampy, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:38.69,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,I was by your side,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:41.99,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,yet I never realized your pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:47.51,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,You've devoted your life to \Nserving the shogun family,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.59,0:12:51.51,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,yet we've only made you suffer for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:56.59,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,Grampy, is it too late to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:12:59.84,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,fulfill your promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:03.63,Main01,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Shigeshige-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:09.40,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,Soyo, take care of Grampy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:11.07,Main01,Soyo,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:13.16,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,Clear a path.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:19.19,Main01,Shige,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk to my uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:21.54,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,The man who raised them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:26.64,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Oboro, what is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:31.44,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Who was the one who turned a helpless,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:37.00,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,fatherless boy into the shogun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:41.84,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Who was the one who kept \Nyou and this nation safe
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:46.00,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,while being accused of \Nselling out this country?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:49.43,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,It was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:53.77,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,I, Tokugawa Sadasada, am \Nthe father of this nation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:58.38,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,My rule has kept this nation safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:03.28,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Despite all that, you now \Nchoose to turn on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:08.56,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,They say that a doll will gain \Na heart if enough time passes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:11.97,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,though it seems that this doll \Nwas given a stubborn soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:18.97,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,He's realized that you were protecting \Nyourself, not this nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.97,0:14:22.22,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,If you continue to \Ncling to this country,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:24.02,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,your position may not \Nbe the only thing lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:26.31,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,You may lose your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:30.05,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,Please join me in seeking \Nhelp from the Tendoshu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:32.51,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to abandon
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:34.26,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,what's taken me half \Nmy life to build up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:39.31,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,To run off to the Tendoshu and \Nallow these traitors to live?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:42.81,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,Considering the contributions \Nyou have made,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:46.11,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,they will surely assist \Nin restoring you to power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:47.58,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:50.78,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,They consider both myself \Nand Shigeshige...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:54.79,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,No, they consider this entire planet \Nto be nothing more than a tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.67,0:14:57.79,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, messenger \Nof the heavens,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:14:59.89,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Yatagarasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:07.55,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,The Tendoshu sent you to ensure that \NI would be an expendable tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:10.42,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,If I am the traitor who \Nsold out this country,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:15.81,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,you Naraku are the crows \Nwho feed on its carcass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:17.99,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,That ship is here to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:19.27,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:21.12,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Once I meet with the Tendoshu,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:24.11,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never return to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:26.77,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,We are ready to take \Nyou wherever you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:32.26,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,Our mission is to assist \Nyou in any way possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:35.58,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,You'll take me wherever I wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:37.14,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:38.62,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,let's go to Yoshiwara!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:43.95,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,The place where my rule began.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:46.88,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,The cursed land where I was betrayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:51.18,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to prove your \Nloyalty to me in that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:54.26,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,Prove our loyalty? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:57.51,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Kill Suzuran.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:01.22,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,That betrayal was where this all began.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:03.73,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,So Maizo and Suzuran...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:11.74,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,I will completely shatter your promise \Nand end this once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:16.74,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,I will punish every person \Nwho dared to betray me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:19.75,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,If that is what you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.77,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,I will follow shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:23.22,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,Set sail for Yoshiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:32.28,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshiwara?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:35.09,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:39.38,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This ship won't take you to paradise...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:42.73,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's headed straight to hell, bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:05.77,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:09.68,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Did he pull it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:12.26,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Gi—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:13.42,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:19.18,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,You refuse to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:23.20,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you to drag that \Nbeaten body back before me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:26.97,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,You continue to fight? \NYou continue to howl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:31.27,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,If you would close your eyes, you \Nwould not suffer any more loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:35.20,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you return to the \Nbattlefield again,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:36.70,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,White Yaksha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:39.20,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.20,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you struggle,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:44.20,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,none of it will come back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:47.27,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,Not this country, not your \Nfriends, not Shoyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.62,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The Tendoshu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:53.21,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,Did they come here after \Nhearing about the revolt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:54.88,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:58.04,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,You're all finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:02.88,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,You are nothing more than a ghost
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:05.23,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,who roams the battlefield in \Nsearch of that which was lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:08.23,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,This is not where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:13.23,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,You will be consumed by the flames \Nof revenge and sent back to hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:14.65,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:21.40,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's trying to prevent me \Nfrom using poison needles?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.84,0:18:32.29,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,He learned my technique just \Nby experiencing it once?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:34.29,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Sent back to hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:37.01,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You must be dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:40.76,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are already \Non a date in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:49.99,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,Do you believe you can use \Nmy own technique against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:52.31,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,My assassination techniques aren't meant
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:54.94,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,to attack enemy pressure points.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:59.43,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,They're meant for controlling my own \Npressure points to maximize my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:02.20,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,I can easily remove any \Npoison from my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:05.20,Main01,Sada,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oboro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:07.71,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:10.72,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hell's too good for that guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:13.65,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems appropriate \Nfor him to be judged
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.13,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,by the laws he created.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:15.84,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:26.97,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need needles to attack \Nyour pressure points!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:55.75,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,It's over, White Yaksha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:19:58.76,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:00.47,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't lost.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:06.26,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My body can still move.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:10.27,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My hand can still reach.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:11.64,Main01,Shoyo,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gintoki,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:14.33,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}look after things for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:17.27,Main01,Shoyo,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't worry. It's no big deal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.89,0:20:20.29,Main01,Shoyo,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be back very soon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:24.28,Main01,Shoyo,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So until then, please protect our friends,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.33,0:20:28.11,Main01,Shoyo,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}protect everyone, for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:35.38,Main01,Shoyo,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Promise me that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:48.05,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.79,0:20:49.95,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:54.98,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:12.53,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to hell, White Yaksha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:21.55,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I have a prior engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:24.05,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I already made reservations,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:27.90,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,so you'll have to wait in hell for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:32.52,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Say hello to Sensei for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:35.47,Main01,Oboro,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:09.52,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Promises shouldn't be made lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.71,0:23:49.38,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, so when in summer is \Nthe movie coming out?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:51.26,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Summer's a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.26,0:23:55.79,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid, summer is the period \Nwhen TUBE is active.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.79,0:23:58.60,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So the movie can only be released \Nwhen Maeda's feeling up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.60,0:23:59.87,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.87,0:24:04.88,Ep Title,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,Unsetting Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.88,0:24:09.92,Side Bar Top,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,The Courtesan of a Nation arc
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.88,0:24:09.92,Side Bar Bottom,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,ends next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.92,0:24:14.89,Side Bar Top,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Will the promises that were made
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.92,0:24:14.89,Side Bar Bottom,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,be fulfilled...?
